{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-lecture-template-tsx","path":"/lecture/운영체제/2023-03-07-File-Protection/","result":{"data":{"allMarkdownRemark":{"edges":[{"node":{"html":"<h2 id=\"file-protection\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#file-protection\" aria-label=\"file protection permalink\" class=\"anchor-header before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"20\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"20\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>📌file protection</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>파일에 대한 부적절한 접근 방지</li>\n<li>다중 사용자 시스템에서 더욱 필요</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"제어할-연산들\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EC%A0%9C%EC%96%B4%ED%95%A0-%EC%97%B0%EC%82%B0%EB%93%A4\" aria-label=\"제어할 연산들 permalink\" class=\"anchor-header before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"20\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"20\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>📌제어할 연산들</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>read</li>\n<li>write</li>\n<li>execute</li>\n<li>append</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"file-protection-mechanism\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#file-protection-mechanism\" aria-label=\"file protection mechanism permalink\" class=\"anchor-header before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"20\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"20\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>📌file protection mechanism</h2>\n<h3 id=\"password-기법\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#password-%EA%B8%B0%EB%B2%95\" aria-label=\"password 기법 permalink\" class=\"anchor-header before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"20\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"20\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>📖password 기법</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>각 파일에 passwd 부여</li>\n<li>비현실적(각 파일마다 다른 pw 기억필요, 연산 종류마다 다른 pw 필요)</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"access-matrix-기법\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#access-matrix-%EA%B8%B0%EB%B2%95\" aria-label=\"access matrix 기법 permalink\" class=\"anchor-header before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"20\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"20\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>📖access matrix 기법</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>범위(domain)와 개체(object)사이의 접근 권한을 명시</li>\n<li>Object\n<ul>\n<li>접근 대상 (file, device 등 HW/SW objects)</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>Domain (protection domain)\n<ul>\n<li>접근 권한의 집합</li>\n<li>같은 권한을 가지는 그룹 (사용자, 프로세스)</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>Access right - &#x3C;object-name, rights-set>\r\n<img src=\"https://velog.velcdn.com/images/wjdtmfgh/post/e2b26259-5308-49f6-88d0-03e09e0d8f8d/image.png\" alt=\"\"></li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"implement-access-matrix\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#implement-access-matrix\" aria-label=\"implement access matrix permalink\" class=\"anchor-header before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"20\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"20\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>💻implement access matrix</h2>\n<h3 id=\"global-table\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#global-table\" aria-label=\"global table permalink\" class=\"anchor-header before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"20\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"20\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>🚀global table</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>위 설명 그대로 전체 파일들에 대한 권한을 테이블로 유지</li>\n<li>large table size\r\n<img src=\"https://velog.velcdn.com/images/wjdtmfgh/post/94994077-1000-4c78-b629-bc87e42c6ac5/image.png\" alt=\"\"></li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"access-list\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#access-list\" aria-label=\"access list permalink\" class=\"anchor-header before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"20\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"20\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>🚀access list</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>access matrix의 열을 list로 표현</li>\n<li>즉, 각 object기준으로 각 object가 어떤 domain에대해 어느정도 권한이 있는지 list로 표현</li>\n<li>object 생성 시 각 domain에 대한 권한 설정</li>\n<li>연산에 접근할때 마다 권한을 확인해야 함</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"capability-list\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#capability-list\" aria-label=\"capability list permalink\" class=\"anchor-header before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"20\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"20\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>🚀Capability List</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>Access matrix의 행을 list로 표현</li>\n<li>즉, 각 domain기준으로 각 domain이 어떤 object에대해 어느정도 권한이 있는지 list로 표현</li>\n<li>시스템이 Capability List 보호 해야함</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"lock-key-mechanism\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#lock-key-mechanism\" aria-label=\"lock key mechanism permalink\" class=\"anchor-header before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"20\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"20\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>🚀Lock-key Mechanism</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>Access list와 Capability list를 혼합한 개념</li>\n<li>Object는 Lock을, Domain은 Key를 가짐\n<ul>\n<li>Lock/key : unique bit patterns</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>Domain 내 프로세스가 object에 접근 시, 자시의 key와 object의 lock 짝이 맞아야 함</li>\n<li>시스템은 key list를 관리해야 함</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"implement-access-matrix-방법들-비교\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#implement-access-matrix-%EB%B0%A9%EB%B2%95%EB%93%A4-%EB%B9%84%EA%B5%90\" aria-label=\"implement access matrix 방법들 비교 permalink\" class=\"anchor-header before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"20\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"20\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>📚implement access matrix 방법들 비교</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>Global table\n<ul>\n<li>Simple, but can be large</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>Access list\n<ul>\n<li>Object 별 권한 관리가 용이함</li>\n<li>모든 접근 마다 권한을 검사해야 함, Object 많이 접근하는 경우 느림</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>Capability list\n<ul>\n<li>List내 object들에 대한 접근에 유리</li>\n<li>Object 별 권한 관리(권한 취소 등)가 어려움</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"️실제-os가-많이-쓰는-방법\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EF%B8%8F%EC%8B%A4%EC%A0%9C-os%EA%B0%80-%EB%A7%8E%EC%9D%B4-%EC%93%B0%EB%8A%94-%EB%B0%A9%EB%B2%95\" aria-label=\"️실제 os가 많이 쓰는 방법 permalink\" class=\"anchor-header before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"20\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"20\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>❗️실제 OS가 많이 쓰는 방법</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>Access list와 Capability list 개념을 함께 사용</li>\n<li>domain이 Object에 대한 첫 접근 → access list 탐색\n<ul>\n<li>접근 허용 시, Capability 생성, 이후 접근 시에는 Capability로 빠르게 권한 검사 가능</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>마지막 접근 후 → Capability 삭제</li>\n</ul>","tableOfContents":"<ul>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"#file-protection\">📌file protection</a></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"#%EC%A0%9C%EC%96%B4%ED%95%A0-%EC%97%B0%EC%82%B0%EB%93%A4\">📌제어할 연산들</a></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"#file-protection-mechanism\">📌file protection mechanism</a></p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"#password-%EA%B8%B0%EB%B2%95\">📖password 기법</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#access-matrix-%EA%B8%B0%EB%B2%95\">📖access matrix 기법</a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"#implement-access-matrix\">💻implement access matrix</a></p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"#global-table\">🚀global table</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#access-list\">🚀access list</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#capability-list\">🚀Capability List</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#lock-key-mechanism\">🚀Lock-key Mechanism</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#implement-access-matrix-%EB%B0%A9%EB%B2%95%EB%93%A4-%EB%B9%84%EA%B5%90\">📚implement access matrix 방법들 비교</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#%EF%B8%8F%EC%8B%A4%EC%A0%9C-os%EA%B0%80-%EB%A7%8E%EC%9D%B4-%EC%93%B0%EB%8A%94-%EB%B0%A9%EB%B2%95\">❗️실제 OS가 많이 쓰는 방법</a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>","frontmatter":{"title":"File Protection","date":"2023년 03월 06일","tags":["CS"]}}}]}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/lecture/운영체제/2023-03-07-File-Protection/","previous":{"fields":{"slug":"/lecture/운영체제/2023-03-06-Disk-System/"},"frontmatter":{"categories":["운영체제"],"title":"Disk System","date":"2023-03-06 01:00:00 +0900","tags":["CS"]}},"next":{"fields":{"slug":"/lecture/운영체제/2023-03-07-Directory-Structure/"},"frontmatter":{"categories":["운영체제"],"title":"Directory Structure","date":"2023-03-07 01:00:00 +0900","tags":["CS"]}}}},"staticQueryHashes":[],"slicesMap":{}}